      "review_text": "So me and my husband were playing and it was fine at first but halfway through the second day the power went out and we couldnt find the power box anywhere. And i needed more stock for the store and tried to order something but had no clue where the wearhouse even was. It would be nice if they told you about this stuff in the tutorial or when you do order something or when something like a power outage happens.",
