      "author_steamid": "76561198218657020",
      "voted_up": true,
      "votes_up": 2,
      "playtime_at_review": 60,
      "review_text": "To be honest i first thought this would be like the other \"simulators\" that are pretty much one and the same, but this one really did surprise me positively. I liked the mechanics and all. Its rather simplistic and things like cleaning could be a bit better, but all in all its reall nice. I will totally buy the full game. I can really highly recommend it",
      "timestamp_created": 1773836295
    },
    {
      "review_id": "221196563",
      "author_steamid": "76561199487776183",
      "voted_up": false,
      "votes_up": 1,
      "playtime_at_review": 28,
      "review_text": "I spent some time playing this free game to see if it’s worth checking out, and overall, it lands right in the middle. The gameplay loop is very basic: clean, restock, refuel, repeat. It works, but it doesn’t really evolve into anything more.\n\nA few things stood out:\n\nRepetitive tasks with little progression\nNPCs reuse the same voice lines (which gets annoying fast)\nMinimal depth or variation in gameplay\nEasy to pick up, but not very engaging long-term\n\nThat said, it’s not all bad. If you’re just looking to kill time or want something low-effort to play while relaxing, it does the job.\n\n🎮 Final Verdict: 5/10\n\nA decent time-waster, but not something I’d go out of my way to recommend. Play it if you’re bored—skip it if you’re looking for something more engaging.\n\nCheck out my playthrough on you tube- \nhttps://youtu.be/gxBiPK_oOdo\n\n",
      "timestamp_created": 1774038973
